WEBVTT

00:00:07.204 --> 00:00:09.746
Think back to a really vivid memory.

00:00:09.788 --> 00:00:10.871
Got it?

00:00:10.913 --> 00:00:15.871
Okay, now try to remember
what you had for lunch three weeks ago.

00:00:15.913 --> 00:00:17.996
That second memory
probably isn't as strong,

00:00:18.038 --> 00:00:19.329
but why not?

00:00:19.371 --> 00:00:22.329
Why do we remember
some things, and not others?

00:00:22.371 --> 00:00:25.371
And why do memories eventually fade?

